subproject.description:
1) Policy recommendation for energy standards and labels in thailand and MEPs information for BRESL products to eliminate low efficiency and promote high efficiency energy consuming products in the appliance market; 
2) Improved institutional and individual capacity to implement ES&L and Carbon Footprint programmes;
3) Increased access to information for, and enhanced technical knowledge of local appliance/equipment manufacturers of EE products; 
4) Enhanced regional cooperation and information sharing on ES&L procedures and protocal; 
5) Increased confidence of appliance/equipment users on teh effectiveness of ES&L programmes.

